WildCards : Special Characters
* : matches any number of Characters
? : matches exact one Character
[] : matchesany one of enclosed Character
{} : matches a group of characters 


Find files endingor starting with Some Extension {
ls *Extension : * can be any character or group of characters
ls ?Extension : ? is any one character
}

Create/list/delete any number of files {
    touch filename{1...Number}
    ls filanme{1..Number}
    rm filename{1..Number}
}

Find files with exact N number of characters name {
    ls ??..Ntimes
}

Find files with name starting or ending with A or B or C etc {
    ls [ABC]* : A,B,C can be letter,numbers or symbols
}

Find File with Numeric/Alphabets Values in Name {
    ls *[0-9]*
    ls *[A-Z]*
    ls *[a-z]*
}


